item.description:
Video from tonight&rsquo;s concert featuring the Comal Community Band and the Canyon Cougar Balladiers for the New Braunfels Music Study Club at the Cross Lutheran Church Gym (February 1, 2018).
This was taken with my phone from the stage, so the audio is a bit overdone at particularly loud parts. Also this was my first Youtube Live&hellip;
